    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到《冰雪卡车司机》（<strong>Ice Truckers</strong>），这是一款身临其境的模拟运输游戏，游戏的背景设定在环境恶劣的偏远北极岛屿上。控制多用途卡车，同时面对动态和不断变化的天气条件。在令人惊叹的开放世界中，为不同公司运送货物，用专用车辆扩充车队，完成动态运送任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395960/extras/2ac0d29a35e1cf567196500a6c2194d3.poster.avif?t=1757587803\" width=572 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395960/extras/2ac0d29a35e1cf567196500a6c2194d3.webm?t=1757587803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395960/extras/2ac0d29a35e1cf567196500a6c2194d3.mp4?t=1757587803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 256 平方公里的广阔开放世界中航行，动态天气和时间的变化让您时刻保持警惕。从茂密的森林到广袤的冰冻苔原，这座岛屿的每个角落都蕴藏着新的挑战和机遇。暴风雪、暴风雪和冰雪覆盖的道路只是阻挡你到达目的地的部分障碍。动态天气系统确保没有两次旅行是相同的，让您时刻保持警惕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395960/extras/aa118c448e7b2378fc0e6698dc8ed050.poster.avif?t=1757587803\" width=800 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395960/extras/aa118c448e7b2378fc0e6698dc8ed050.webm?t=1757587803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395960/extras/aa118c448e7b2378fc0e6698dc8ed050.mp4?t=1757587803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驾驶装载着不同拖车和货物的大型重载卡车，在最艰险的地形上行驶，感受卡车的重量和动力。冰雪卡车司机》中有各种卡车，每种卡车都有自己的操控特性，并具有第一人称视角或第三人称视角。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >花费您辛苦赚来的现金，扩大您的车队，确保每项任务都有合适的车辆！扩建您的总部，优化您的运营，为另一项任务画上圆满句号！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395960/extras/f4434a64e014b28ac6149fb0724629a0.poster.avif?t=1757587803\" width=636 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395960/extras/f4434a64e014b28ac6149fb0724629a0.webm?t=1757587803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2395960/extras/f4434a64e014b28ac6149fb0724629a0.mp4?t=1757587803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过完成各种关键任务，从向偏远的研究站运送必需品到帮助公司增加利润，与有趣的角色打交道，提高您在不同派别中的地位。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过提高您在争夺该地区控制权的各家公司中的声望，解锁新的车辆、货物和任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您的货物对于那些与世隔绝在严酷北方荒野中的人们的生存至关重要。每成功运送一次货物，就能让岛上居民的生活更上一层楼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特点</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种不同的卡车、拖车和货物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >详细的车辆内饰和外饰</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面积达 256 平方米的大型开放世界岛屿，岛上地形多变，天气和昼夜交替变化多端</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >考验驾驶技能和决策能力的挑战性任务</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有复杂声誉系统的不同公司和派系</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可瞬间改变任务进程的随机事件，例如阻塞道路的雪崩、抛锚的汽车或路边的尸体</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are you ready to get in your truck and take over the frozen north with your driving skills? Your Arctic Adventure awaits!</strong></p>",
